A MajorMode for editing [WikiPedia:Ada_%28programming_language%29 Ada] programs comes with Emacs.

Project page:

* http://stephe-leake.org/emacs/ada-mode/emacs-ada-mode.html

The current [::ada-mode] maintainer is StephenLeake,[http://stephe-leake.org/] who maintains the code in GNU Emacs and periodically publishes updated versions on the project page.

The ada-mode distribution contains gpr-mode.el, a major mode for editing GNAT project files (.gpr).

ElseMode comes with templates for writing Ada source code.

